comments: Alvarado (NOP) establishes himself in a legal screening position in the path of Wright (ATL) and some incidental contact occurs during the screen.
Valanciunas (NOP) momentarily grasps the back of Capela's (ATL) jersey and relinquishes it without impacting Capela's range of motion.
Capela (ATL) reaches in and briefly grasps Valanciunas' (NOP) left arm while attempting to get two hands to the ball.
McCollum (NOP) and Wright (ATL) engage and disengage prior to the screen.
Capela (ATL) makes contact with Valanciuas' (NOP) hand after the release of the fadeaway post shot attempt. Any 'high-five' contact after the release is considered incidental.
Young (ATL) drives to the middle of the paint with Alvarado (NOP) on his hip and some marginal contact occurs as Young stops and his off-arm comes out slightly and brushes Alvarado.
Young (ATL) veers into and creates contact with Alverado (NOP) on the drive and affects his ability to defend on the play.

Valanciunas (NOP) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Young (ATL) and some marginal contact occurs as the latter goes under the screen. Young's reaction is not consistent wit the level of contact.
Capela (ATL) establishes himself in a legal screening position in the path of Jones (NOP) and some marginal contact occurs as Capela is firming up when setting the screen.

Gallinari (ATL) establishes himself in a screening position in the desired path of Jones (NOP), and some marginal contact occurs to the trailing defender as Gallinari turns his body slightly. The contact does not impact the defensive play.
Valanciunas (NOP) turns his body in the air and body contact occurs with Young (ATL) that affects the driving shot attempt.
Wright (ATL) legally contests McCollum's (NOP) running floater in the paint.
Young (ATL) steps upwards and into the path of Alvarado (NOP) and bumps his shoulder, which impacts the dribbler's SQBR.
Capela (ATL) establishes himself in a legal screening position in the path of Alvarado (NOP) and absorbs the contact to his chest as the defender moves into the legal screen.
Hayes (NOP) legally contests the jump shot attempt from Gallinari (ATL).
Bogdanovic (ATL) commits a take foul on Valanciunas (NOP).
Bogdanovic (ATL) establishes himself in a screening position and extends his arms slightly into McCollum (NOP) as he turns to relocate and the contact is marginal.
McCollum (NOP) legally contests the jump shot attempt from Bogdanovic (ATL)
